  "text": "One study, from the United Kingdom [CITATION_1] , of 204 sudden deaths in residential care over a 50 year period found one case of suicide from jumping from a bridge. Another study of mortality over 60 years, from a large US residential care center in California (21), did not report any case of suicide.",
